s voice to the ongoing demands of Nigerians against Police brutality and Police reforms via social media. The post #EndSARS: 'We may never have another in this lifetime' – Timi Dakolo appeared first on Most Trusted Voice in Music & Afrobeats from Nigeria & Africa | Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.